  "description": "<p><strong>Work Location: 6 Tampines Industrial Avenue 5 Singapore 528760<br>\nWork Day: 4 Days work, 3 days off. 3 Days work, 4 Days off. Need to work one weekend.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Work Time<br>\nMorning Shift : 7am - 7pm<br>\nNight Shift : 7pm - 7am</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Receiving, transferring and dispatching parts/materials</li>\n  <li>Examine incoming parts/materials for damage/shortages and take necessary action</li>\n  <li>Report any errors or faults of products/goals to superiors</li>\n  <li>Assemble the products to the required specifications and standards</li>\n  <li>Other related tasks when required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min primary / secondary school</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1-2 years of relevant production experience / relevant industries</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Compliance with RBA standards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
